<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Kiaphith Stormspire</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-31 02:52:34</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I found this POS off a named Gnoll in South Karana.  He spawns in the same ruins that Lord Grimrot does, but is around lv 17.  He's a necromancer and has a pet, but can be dropped with little trouble using decent nukes.  You will want to kill him quick because his DoT's and fear can be a real pain.  I simply root his pet (uncommon for Druids, but it works better than kiting in this instance), and hammer him with Careless lightning a few time.  He has around 300hp generally.  He also drops a few other things, including his head which is used for the monks' red headband quest or some such.<BR>
<BR>
Hope this helps; but why anyone would actually camp a Mob for this is beyond me.</font></td></tr></table>
